## Testing Checklist

Before submitting changes:
- [ ] `flutter analyze` shows 0 issues
- [ ] `flutter run` launches without errors
- [ ] Custom room creation works end-to-end
- [ ] Custom device creation works end-to-end
- [ ] Device-specific questions appear for tested device types
- [ ] Risk score updates when questions are answered
- [ ] Device-specific actions appear in evaluation screen
- [ ] UI text is German throughout
- [ ] Material 3 teal theme is applied consistently

## Troubleshooting

### "The name 'currentRoom' is already defined"
- Duplicate getter/property in screen class
- Check for duplicate method definitions

### ".withOpacity is deprecated"
- Replace with `.withValues(alpha: x)`
- Example: `Colors.teal.withValues(alpha: 0.1)`

### Device-specific questions not appearing
- Check `DeviceTemplate.deviceType` matches string used in `DeviceInstance.questions`
- Verify question added to `CatalogData.getDeviceSpecificQuestions()`
- Check conditional logic: `if (template.deviceType == 'speaker')`

### Custom devices not showing in grid
- Verify `_AddDeviceCard` widget is defined
- Check grid logic: `allDevices.length + state.customDevices.length + 1`
- Ensure `isCustom` flag is properly set

